                    <li class="nav-item" style="margin-left: 800px;">
                        <a class="btn bg-black text-white float-right" href="/contact">Contact</a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>
    <div class="container-fluid d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center">
        <div class="card mt-5 bg-semi default-shadow">
            <div class="card-body d-flex">
                <div class="greeting d-flex-row ms-2 mr-2" style="width: 600px;">
                    <h2 class="title">Hi, Welcome to My Hut!</h2>
                    <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Culpa, quo! Debitis excepturi veniam, provident blanditiis enim voluptas laborum in similique saepe tempora aut, ea ipsam quas quod iure perspiciatis id! Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Minus doloremque quas esse placeat accusantium dolore provident quaerat maiores iste! Incidunt repudiandae minima autem sed aperiam iure similique fuga, maiores quam? Lorem, ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Rerum delectus porro esse fugiat tempore quidem magnam reiciendis eveniet ex, soluta dolorum eum consequatur cumque est quae ipsam molestiae facere ea?</p>
                    <div class="contact-me d-flex">
                        <a href="#" style="font-weight:600" class="btn bg-black text-white mr-2 mb-4 mt-2">Contact Me</a>
                        <a href="https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1xb9c-bqpvQBGzn06gkaREE7KLrAKWrWQ?usp=sharing" style="color:black;font-weight:600" class="nav-link mr-2 mb-4 mt-1">Download CV</a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="socmed d-flex"> 
                      <a class="mr-4" href="https://www.instagram.com/"><img src="../assets/pic/instagram-logo.png" alt="instagram" style="width:40px"></a>
                      <a class="mr-4" href="https://www.facebook.com/"><img src="assets/pic/facebook-logo.png" alt="facebook" style="width:40px"></a>
                      <a class="mr-4" href="https://www.linkedin.com/"><img src="assets/pic/linkedin-logo.png" alt="linkedin" style="width:40px"></a>
                      <a class="mr-4" href="https://www.twitter.com/"><img src="assets/pic/twitter-logo.png" alt="twitter" style="width:40px"></a>
                    </div>
                </div>
              <div class="card" style="width: 300px;">
                <img class="card-img-top" src="assets/pic/new foto profil.jpg" alt="Foto Profil">
                <div class="card-body">
                  <p class="title" style="text-align:center;">Moh Zulfikar Rofi Yansyah</p>
                  <p class="title" style="text-align:center;">Fullstack Developer</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
    </div>
    <div class="container-fluid mt-5 p-5 bg-semi">
        <h2 class="title mt-2 mb-5" style="text-align: center;">MY PROJECT</h2>
        <div class="d-flex flex-wrap">
            <div class="card-deck p-3">
                {{#each projects}}
                <div class="card default-shadow p-2">
                    <img class="card-img-top" src="assets/pic/coding.jpg" alt="Card image cap">
                  <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="title">{{this.pname}}</h5>
                    <p class="passive-text">{{this.durasi}}</p>
                    <p class="text-fill">{{this.description}}</p>
                    <div class="tech-logo">
                        {{#if this.node}}<i class="fa-brands fa-node-js"></i>{{/if}}
                        {{#if this.vue}}<i class="fa-brands fa-vuejs"></i>{{/if}}
                        {{#if this.react}}<i class="fa-brands fa-react"></i>{{/if}}
                        {{#if this.bootstrap}}<i class="fa-brands fa-bootstrap"></i>{{/if}}
                    </div>
                    <div class="d-flex mt-2 mb-2">
                        <a href="update/{{@index}}" class="btn bg-black text-white default-shadow mr-3">Edit</a>
                        <a href="delete-project/{{@index}}" class="btn bg-black text-white default-shadow">Delete</a>
                    </div>
                    <p class="card-text"><small class="text-muted">Last updated 3 mins ago</small></p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                {{/each}}
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.0-beta1/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-pprn3073KE6tl6bjs2QrFaJGz5/SUsLqktiwsUTF55Jfv3qYSDhgCecCxMW52nD2" crossorigin="anonymous"></script> 
</body>
</html>